It is assumed that people have the same skills to participate in the digital age.  --> Update: This was important for me because many immigrants with whom I worked with previously had limited technological skills.  At most they had completed some grade school and had never worked with computers, know how to text, etc.  It is not just to be assumed that the elder encounter this issue but it is widely applicable.

Did not receive adequate care at the hospital. --> Update: This was important because it shows the neglect this individual faced at a hospital in a time of care, it seems that others in this conversation shared similar frustrations.
